content: समि {c2c} <ab>P.</ab> {@--1@} To come or meet together, be united or joined with. {@--2@} To go or come to, arrive at, approach, reach, visit, attain. {@--3@} To encounter, meet in a hostile manner. {@--4@} To cohabit, have sexual intercourse. {@--5@} To enter upon, commence. {@--6@} To agree with.
